  "Martin Naughton is the owner of Glen Dimplex, a manufacturer of consumer appliances like washing machines, hair dryers and space heaters.",
  "As a student, Naughton spent months in hands-on aeronautical and mechanical engineering training.",
  "He founded Glen Electric with a handful of people in 1973 and started off selling oil-filled radiators.",
  "Four years later he acquired the much larger British heating company Dimplex, renaming it Glen Dimplex.",
  "Naughton stepped down as president in April 2016 and his youngest son Fergal took over as CEO. "
